"title": "2422: gospel, confirmation of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2422: gospel, confirmation of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The trustworthiness of the gospel of Jesus Christ rests upon the fulfilment of OT prophecies concerning Jesus Christ, the apostolic witness to Jesus Christ and the divine witness to Jesus Christ during his ministry, culminating in his resurrection.</p>\n<h2>Prophecies of the OT concerning Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Fulfilment of prophecy recognised by Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:54-Matt26:56\">MAT 26:54–26:56</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:24\">MAT 26:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:31\">MAT 26:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:21\">LUK 4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:22\">LUK 21:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:25-Luke24:27\">LUK 24:25–24:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:44\">LUK 24:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:46\">LUK 24:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:18\">JHN 13:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:9\">PSA 41:9</a></p>\n<h3>Fulfilment of prophecy recognised by NT speakers and writers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:21\">ROM 3:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:68-Luke1:70\">LUK 1:68–1:70</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:18\">ACT 3:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:43\">ACT 10:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:22\">ACT 26:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:2\">ROM 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:3-1Cor15:5\">1CO 15:3–15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:10-1Pet1:12\">1PE 1:10–1:12</a>MAT <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:22-1Pet1:23\">1:22–1:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:14\">ISA 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:5-Matt2:6\">MAT 2:5–2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:2\">MIC 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:15\">MAT 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos11:1\">HOS 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:17-Matt2:18\">MAT 2:17–2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:15\">JER 31:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:23\">MAT 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:14-Matt4:16\">MAT 4:14–4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:1-Isa9:2\">ISA 9:1–9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:17\">MAT 8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:4\">ISA 53:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:17-Matt12:21\">MAT 12:17–12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1-Isa42:4\">ISA 42:1–42:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:4-Matt21:5\">MAT 21:4–21:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9\">ZEC 9:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:9-Matt27:10\">MAT 27:9–27:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:24\">JHN 19:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:18\">PSA 22:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:28\">JHN 19:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:36\">JHN 19:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:46\">EXO 12:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:37\">JHN 19:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:10\">ZEC 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:25-Acts2:28\">ACT 2:25–2:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:8-Ps16:11\">PSA 16:8–16:11</a></p>\n<h3>Realisation of types</h3>\n<p>The sign of Jonah:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:38-Matt12:41\">MAT 12:38–12:41</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:29-Luke11:32\">LUK 11:29–11:32</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:4\">MAT 16:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:31-John6:35\">JHN 6:31–6:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:48-John6:51\">JHN 6:48–6:51</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:1-Heb3:6\">HEB 3:1–3:6</a> <em>Jesus Christ as the greater Moses</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb6:20-Heb7:10\">HEB 6:20–7:10</a> <em>Jesus Christ as the high priest after the order of Melchizedek</em></p>\n<h3>Fulfilment of ceremony and sacrifice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:29\">JHN 1:29</a></strong> <em>Jesus Christ fulfils all that the sacrificial system stood for.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:6-Heb9:14\">HEB 9:6–9:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:18-1Pet1:19\">1PE 1:18–1:19</a></p>\n<h2>Witness of the apostles to Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:35\">JHN 19:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:48\">LUK 24:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:27\">JHN 15:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:24\">JHN 21:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:32\">ACT 2:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:20\">ACT 4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:32\">ACT 5:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:31\">ACT 13:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:1\">1PE 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1-1John1:2\">1JN 1:1–1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:14\">1JN 4:14</a></p>\n<h2>Witness of God the Father to his Son</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt3:16-Matt3:17\">MAT 3:16–3:17</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:9-Mark1:11\">MRK 1:9–1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:21-Luke3:22\">LUK 3:21–3:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:32-John1:34\">JHN 1:32–1:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:5\">MAT 17:5</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:7\">MRK 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:35\">LUK 9:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:23-John12:32\">JHN 12:23–12:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:17-2Pet1:18\">2PE 1:17–1:18</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ vindicated by his resurrection</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:1-Rom1:4\">ROM 1:1–1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:24-Acts2:28\">ACT 2:24–2:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:8-Ps16:11\">PSA 16:8–16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:30-Acts13:35\">ACT 13:30–13:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:31\">ACT 17:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:11\">ROM 8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:9\">ROM 10:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:14-1Cor15:15\">1CO 15:14–15:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:21\">1PE 1:21</a></p>\n<h2>Warnings against false gospels</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:6-Gal1:9\">GAL 1:6–1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:11\">1CO 3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:1-1John4:3\">1JN 4:1–4:3</a></p>",
